## High-Level Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    User[User] --> React[React Frontend]
    React --> API[FastAPI Backend]

    API --> Auth[JWT Auth Middleware]
    API --> SessionDB[(PostgreSQL)]
    API --> Upload[Document Upload Service]

    Upload --> Parser[Document Parser]
    Parser --> Chunker[Text Chunker]
    Chunker --> Embed[OpenAI Embeddings]
    Embed --> Pinecone[(Pinecone Vector DB)]

    API --> Graph[LangGraph Agent Workflow]

    Graph --> Retrieve[Retrieve Documents]
    Retrieve --> Pinecone
    Retrieve --> Grade[Grade Relevance]

    Grade --> Decision{Relevant?}
    Decision -->|Yes| Rerank[Re-rank Chunks]
    Decision -->|No| Rewrite[Rewrite Query]
    Rewrite --> Retrieve

    Decision -->|Fallback Needed| Tools[Tools: Web Search / Calculator / SQL]

    Rerank --> Generate[Generate Answer]
    Tools --> Generate

    Generate --> Citations[Attach Sources + Confidence]
    Citations --> React
```

---

## Core RAG Flow

```text
Question
   ↓
Create query embedding
   ↓
Search Pinecone
   ↓
Retrieve top-k document chunks
   ↓
Grade relevance
   ↓
Re-rank best chunks
   ↓
Generate answer
   ↓
Return answer with citations
```

---

## Corrective RAG Flow

```text
User Question
      ↓
Retrieve documents from Pinecone
      ↓
Grade retrieved documents
      ↓
Are documents relevant?
      ├── Yes
      │     ↓
      │   Generate answer
      │
      └── No
            ↓
          Rewrite query
            ↓
          Retrieve again
            ↓
          Still weak?
            ├── Use fallback search
            └── Ask clarification / say not enough evidence
```

---

## Agentic RAG Flow

```text
User asks question
      ↓
Agent analyzes intent
      ↓
Agent decides next action
      ↓
Possible actions:
  - Retrieve documents
  - Rewrite query
  - Use web search
  - Use calculator
  - Query database
  - Ask clarification
  - Generate final answer
      ↓
Agent loops until answer is ready
      ↓
Final answer with sources
```

